query:
ALTER TABLE nozzleEvaluations 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS service VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS pipeOutsideDiameter DECIMAL(10,4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS manufacturingTolerance DECIMAL(5,4) DEFAULT 0.125,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS toleranceOverridden BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS previousThickness DECIMAL(10,4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nominalThickness DECIMAL(10,4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS reinforcementRequired DECIMAL(10,4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS reinforcementAvailable DECIMAL(10,4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS reinforcementAdequate BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS reinforcementMargin DECIMAL(10,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS shortTermCorrosionRate DECIMAL(10,6),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS longTermCorrosionRate DECIMAL(10,6),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS corrosionRate DECIMAL(10,6),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS corrosionRateType ENUM('LT', 'ST', 'USER', 'GOVERNING'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS remainingLife DECIMAL(10,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nextInspectionDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS currentInspectionDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS previousInspectionDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS originalInstallDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS governingCriterion ENUM('pipe_schedule', 'shell_head_required', 'reinforcement'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS calculationNotes TEXT;
